  "texts": [
    "[5.299] \"I don't want to break your heart, Ron\", says Chris.",
    "[3,312] 'I only know that my heart is jumping all over the place and I really think I love you too.'",
    "[2,337] Will snapped at Enid in a way he had never done before, because a knot of worry was tearing his heart.",
    "[2,379] What she saw stopped the heart in her throat.",
    "[2,395] They just stood and waited till the noise was abated slightly, by which time Doris was shaking from head to foot."
